{"type": "article", "id": 15299, "title": "《The Elements of Typographic Style》", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230603at0F6wyXz58fIcvH.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.70622797\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Elements-Typographic-Style-Version-Anniversary/dp/0881792128/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1442476743&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=The+Elements+of+Typographic+Style\" target=\"_blank\">《The Elements of Typographic Style》</a>，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tRobert Bringhurst, Hartley and Marks Publishers; Fourth Edition, 2013\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一本关于文字设计（typography）的风格手册，Robert Bringhurst 不是一般的工具书作者，他是诗人和翻译家。不管你对于文字设计有没有兴趣，都可以从 Bringhurst 的文字中感受到一种工整与精深的穿透力。而这只是风格手册「而已」。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><em>关于作者：不鸟万如一，「好奇心日报」特约驻美记者，IPN 播客网络联合创始人，《 IT 公论》主播。</em></span><em></em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}